eu.amidst.core.exponentialfamily

Interface MomentParameters

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Vector
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArrayVector, CompoundVector, EF_Normal_NormalParents.CompoundVector, EF_Normal.ArrayVectorParameter, EF_NormalParameter.ArrayVectorParameter, KeyCompoundVector

    public interface MomentParameters
extends Vector
    This interface extends the interface Vector and handles classes for representing the moment parameter vector of an exponential family distribution in canonical form.

    For further details about how exponential family models are considered in this toolbox, take a look at the following paper: Representation, Inference and Learning of Bayesian Networks as Conjugate Exponential Family Models. Technical Report. (pdf)
